[Experiment] **Exponential warmup + cosine decay + reduced weight decay (0.05) + EMA + beta2=0.99**

Combine the best schedule with lower weight decay (0.05 instead of 0.1). The strong regularization from EMA may allow for less explicit L2 regularization, enabling better training data fitting while maintaining good generalization through EMA averaging.

